<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Handlebars Node Demo</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #0a0f1e;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: #111827;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #1e2d46;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .btn-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .btn {
            background: #1e293b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: block;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #3b82f6;
            border-color: #60a5fa;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Node.js &amp; Handlebars</h1>
        <p>This demo uses Express to render the .hbs templates severely using server-side logic and dummy data.</p>

        <div class="btn-grid">
            <a href="/invoice" target="_blank" class="btn">🧾 View Invoice</a>
            <a href="/payslip" target="_blank" class="btn">💼 View Payslip</a>
            <a href="/purchase-order" target="_blank" class="btn">📦 View Purchase Order</a>
            <a href="/quotation" target="_blank" class="btn">💬 View Quotation</a>
            <a href="/billing-details" target="_blank" class="btn">🏦 View Billing Details</a>
            <a href="/custom-template" target="_blank" class="btn">🛠️ View Custom Template</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>